<span class="go">|  1.20|  3.45|</span>
<span class="go">|1.20  |3.45  |</span>
<span class="go">|   foo|     b|</span>
<span class="go">|foo   |b     |</span>
<span class="go">a string</span>
<span class="go">an error</span>
</pre></div>

          </td>
        </tr>
        
